{"tid":2161614,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"男朋友JJ好短好細","createTime":"2020-08-17T15:58:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-24T07:31:18.000Z","uid":325243,"like":30,"dislike":94,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"00715d4fb0217c42a01b1d28b96d24f5a6d1efc7","tid":2161614,"uid":325243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T15:58:57.000Z","msg":"我仲係處女 可能未必會比第一次比而家呢個男朋友<br />\n但我都介意男朋友果到好短同好細<br />\n初時以為自己冇吸引力 就咁攬住都feel吾到佢勃起 摸佢都吾太硬<br />\n<br />\n勃起左大概一個手掌位 吾計手指淨計手掌<br />\n佢話未比人睇過 加上佢話之前同女朋友做好快就完事<br />\n<br />\n佢自己對呢方面好自卑<br />\n佢大我幾年 又對我真係好好<br />\n啲人話愛佢就會接受佢<br />\n但有啲人就話呢個人要對一世 吾好揀<br />\n雖然未講到話結婚 但係拖佢幾年怕佢再難識到女仔 但心入面都介意佢既長度同快完事<br />\n另一方面如果為左咁同佢分手<br />\n下一個未必會咁珍惜雙方既戀情 大家sis遇到呢個情況又會點諗？"},{"pid":"50be3c60e8f5d538f91124f23ddd650c08008d9c","tid":2161614,"uid":325243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T15:59:19.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"655e409c622f8890df67d7cc9394f0b5591da269","tid":2161614,"uid":188129,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T15:59:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fa99f4ab53cb2c0d1f56a8cc8e85b846b661fe0d","tid":2161614,"uid":168730,"like":137,"dislike":2,"score":135,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T15:59:39.000Z","msg":"你果條大咪得lo<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec1b6fb18db36f4174ebf5663b4a2354515a3125","tid":2161614,"uid":327483,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T16:00:00.000Z","msg":"外表如何？"},{"pid":"e0dec4a5a7f98a8faadaea746908486f9e7d7535","tid":2161614,"uid":332831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T16:00:42.000Z","msg":"分手啦"},{"pid":"b50082f1570efc45b74b77b3d93280cfd4bc0243","tid":2161614,"uid":325243,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"ec1b6fb18db36f4174ebf5663b4a2354515a3125","tid":2161614,"uid":327483,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T16:00:00.000Z","msg":"外表